# Studio Design System — Cursor Rules

## Visual Reference

Before writing any UI code, HTML, or CSS, read the design system file at:

  ./design-system.html

Study the colour swatches, typography scale, spacing tokens, and rendered components before producing any output.

## Using this in another project

Cursor only reads `.cursorrules` from the project root. If this design system lives in a
subfolder (e.g. `./design-system/`), copy the content of this file into your project's
root `.cursorrules` and update the path above to match, e.g.:

  ./design-system/design-system.html

## Typefaces

- Headings / Display: Cormorant Garamond (weights 300, 400, 500, 600) — always load from Google Fonts
- Body / UI / Labels: DM Sans (weights 300, 400, 500) — always load from Google Fonts
- Never substitute system fonts as the primary typeface

## Colour palette (CSS custom property names)

Primary (Warm Stone): --color-primary-50 through --color-primary-600
Secondary (Sage):     --color-secondary-50 through --color-secondary-600
Neutrals:             --color-neutral-0 through --color-neutral-700
Success:              --color-success-light / -base / -text
Warning:              --color-warning-light / -base / -text
Error:                --color-error-light / -base / -text
Info:                 --color-info-light / -base / -text

Never hardcode a colour value. Always reference a custom property.

## Spacing tokens

space-1: 0.25rem  |  space-2: 0.5rem   |  space-3: 0.75rem
space-4: 1rem     |  space-5: 1.25rem  |  space-6: 1.5rem
space-8: 2rem     |  space-10: 2.5rem  |  space-12: 3rem
space-16: 4rem    |  space-20: 5rem    |  space-24: 6rem

## Border radius

--radius-sm: 2px  |  --radius-md: 4px  |  --radius-lg: 6px  |  --radius-full: 9999px
Do not exceed 8px on any component.

## Shadows

All shadows use warm tint: rgba(100, 80, 60, …)
--shadow-xs / --shadow-sm / --shadow-md / --shadow-lg

## Component class inventory

Buttons:   .btn  +  .btn-primary / -secondary / -outline / -ghost / -destructive
           Sizes: .btn-sm / (default) / .btn-lg
Badges:    .badge  +  .badge-neutral / -primary / -secondary / -success / -warning / -error / -info
           Outline: .badge-outline-neutral / -primary / -secondary
Cards:     .card  +  .card-header / .card-body / .card-footer
           Variants: .card-elevated / .card-tinted
Alerts:    .alert  +  .alert-info / -success / -warning / -error
Forms:     .form-field / .form-label / .form-input / .form-select / .form-textarea
           States: .is-error  |  Hints: .form-hint / .form-error-msg
           Controls: .form-check / .form-check-input / .form-check-label
           Toggle: .toggle / .toggle-track (.is-on) / .toggle-thumb / .toggle-label
Tables:    .table-wrap > .ds-table
Charts:    Series palette — #A38572 / #6F9370 / #6B8DB5 / #C99A4E / #B87878 / #9B8DB5

## Design principles

- Refined, airy, client-presentable — premium consultancy aesthetic
- No dark backgrounds unless explicitly requested
- No loud gradients
- Generous whitespace; use spacing tokens liberally
- One .btn-primary per view maximum
